    <entry>
      <title>C的输入输出函数</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/13/c-de-shu-ru-shu-chu-han-shu/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/13/c-de-shu-ru-shu-chu-han-shu/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1）混用"><a href="#1）混用" class="headerlink" title="1）混用"></a>1）混用</h2><h3 id="1-scanf-s-和printf"><a href="#1-scanf-s-和printf" class="headerlink" title="1. scanf_s()和printf()"></a>1. scanf_s()和printf()</h3><ul><li>scanf_s()与scanf()的区别：读取字符串或数组时需要检查边界，例如，scanf(“%s”,st),scanf_s(“%s”,st,10)<h3 id="2-fscanf-s-和fprintf"><a href="#2-fscanf-s-和fprintf" class="headerlink" title="2. fscanf_s()和fprintf()"></a>2. fscanf_s()和fprintf()</h3></li><li>在文件中格式化读取或写入</li></ul><hr><h2 id="2）字符"><a href="#2）字符" class="headerlink" title="2）字符"></a>2）字符</h2><h3 id="1-getch-char-ch-和putch-char-ch"><a href="#1-getch-char-ch-和putch-char-ch" class="headerlink" title="1. getch(char ch)和putch(char ch)"></a>1. getch(char ch)和putch(char ch)</h3><ul><li>缓冲输入输出<h3 id="2-getchar-char-ch-和putchar-char-ch"><a href="#2-getchar-char-ch-和putchar-char-ch" class="headerlink" title="2. getchar(char ch)和putchar(char ch)"></a>2. getchar(char ch)和putchar(char ch)</h3></li><li>标准输入输出<h3 id="3-getc-FILE-stream-和putc-char-ch-FILE-stream"><a href="#3-getc-FILE-stream-和putc-char-ch-FILE-stream" class="headerlink" title="3. getc(FILE* stream)和putc(char ch,FILE* stream)"></a>3. getc(FILE* stream)和putc(char ch,FILE* stream)</h3></li><li>用于在文件中读取或写入字符<h3 id="4-fgetc-FILE-stream-和fputc-char-ch-FILE-stream"><a href="#4-fgetc-FILE-stream-和fputc-char-ch-FILE-stream" class="headerlink" title="4. fgetc(FILE* stream)和fputc(char ch,FILE* stream)"></a>4. fgetc(FILE* stream)和fputc(char ch,FILE* stream)</h3></li><li>用于在文件中读取或写入字符</li><li>3与4的区别：getc()作为宏被调用，fgetc()作为函数被调用。putc()与fputc()无区别。<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">&#x2F;&#x2F; 常用方法char ch &#x3D; getc(stream);putc(ch,stream);<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li></ul><hr><h2 id="3）字符串"><a href="#3）字符串" class="headerlink" title="3）字符串"></a>3）字符串</h2><h3 id="1-gets-s-char-st-size-和puts"><a href="#1-gets-s-char-st-size-和puts" class="headerlink" title="1. gets_s(char* st,size)和puts()"></a>1. gets_s(char* st,size)和puts()</h3><ul><li>标准输入输出<h3 id="2-sscanf-s-和snprintf"><a href="#2-sscanf-s-和snprintf" class="headerlink" title="2. sscanf_s()和snprintf()"></a>2. sscanf_s()和snprintf()</h3></li><li>从字符串数组中格式化读取或格式化写入到字符串数组</li><li>snprintf()第二个参数为格式化写入字符串的边界<h3 id="3-fgets-char-st-int-size-FILE-stream-和fputs-char-st-FILE-stream"><a href="#3-fgets-char-st-int-size-FILE-stream-和fputs-char-st-FILE-stream" class="headerlink" title="3. fgets(char* st,int size,FILE* stream)和fputs(char* st,FILE* stream)"></a>3. fgets(char* st,int size,FILE* stream)和fputs(char* st,FILE* stream)</h3></li><li>用于在文件中读取或写入字符串</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
