        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-qsort-数组排序"><a href="#1-qsort-数组排序" class="headerlink" title="1.qsort()数组排序"></a>1.qsort()数组排序</h2><ul><li>用法： <pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">void qsort(void* base, size_t num, size_t width, int compare(const void*, const void*));<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li>参数：<ol><li>待排序数组，排序之后的结果仍放在这个数组中</li><li>数组中待排序元素数量</li><li>各元素的占用空间大小（单位为字节）</li><li>指向函数的指针，用于确定排序的顺序（需要用户自定义一个比较函数）<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">eg.整数数组排序#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;#include&lt;stdlib.h&gt;int compare(void* a, void* b);int main()&#123;int ar[8] &#x3D; &#123; 4,5,7,2,6,1,8,3 &#125;;qsort(ar, 8, sizeof(int), compare);for (int i &#x3D; 0; i &lt; 8; i++)printf(&quot;%d&quot;, ar[i]);return 0;&#125;int compare(void* a, void* b)&#123;return *(int*)a - *(int*)b;&#x2F;&#x2F;若要降序排列，改为b-a&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">eg.浮点数数组排序#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;#include&lt;stdlib.h&gt;int compare(void* a, void* b);int main()&#123;double ar[8] &#x3D; &#123; 4.2,4.1,7.6,2.9,2.5,1.6,8.3,8.9 &#125;;qsort(ar, 8, sizeof(double), compare);for (int i &#x3D; 0; i &lt; 8; i++)printf(&quot;%.1f\t&quot;, ar[i]);return 0;&#125;int compare(void* a, void* b)&#123;return *(double*)a &gt; *(double*)b;&#x2F;&#x2F;若|a-b|&lt;1，则会发生截断，等于0，认为两数相等。&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="bsearch"><a href="#bsearch" class="headerlink" title="bsearch()"></a>bsearch()</h2></li></ol></li><li>用法：<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">void *bsearch(const void *key, const void *base, size_t nitems, size_t size, int compare(const void *, const void *))<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li>参数：<ol><li>key – 指向要查找的元素的指针，类型转换为 void*。</li><li>base – 指向进行查找的数组的第一个对象的指针，类型转换为 void*。</li><li>nitems – base 所指向的数组中元素的个数。</li><li>size – 数组中每个元素的大小，以字节为单位。</li><li>compare – 用来比较两个元素的函数。 <pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;#include&lt;stdlib.h&gt;int compare(void* a, void* b);int main()&#123;int ar[8] &#x3D; &#123; 4,8,5,6,7,1,3,2 &#125;;qsort(ar, 8, sizeof(int), compare);for (int i &#x3D; 0; i &lt; 8; i++)printf(&quot;%d\n&quot;, ar[i]);int key &#x3D; 9;int* p;p &#x3D; (int*)bsearch(&amp;key, ar, 8, sizeof(int), compare);(p &#x3D;&#x3D; NULL) ? puts(&quot;not found&quot;) : puts(&quot;found&quot;);return 0;&#125;int compare(void* a, void* b)&#123;return *(int*)a - *(int*)b;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li></ol></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
