      <title>递归</title>
      <link href="/2022/10/17/di-gui/"/>
      <url>/2022/10/17/di-gui/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="递归"><a href="#递归" class="headerlink" title="递归"></a>递归</h1><p>eg.  </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;void up_and_down(int);int main(void)&#123;    up_and_down(1);    return 0;&#125;void up_and_down(int n)&#123;    printf(&quot;Level %d: n location %p\n&quot;, n, &amp;n);     if (n &lt; 4)        up_and_down(n+1);&#x2F;&#x2F;函数执行该语句及之前的语句，然后不断按顺序参数[^1]重复，知道不满足条件n&lt;4    printf(&quot;LEVEL %d: n location %p\n&quot;, n, &amp;n); &#x2F;&#x2F; n&#x3D;4后，函数按逆序参数[^2]重复执行该语句与之后的语句    &#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>Tip:  </p><ul><li>递归必须有出口。eg. n&lt;4   </li><li>递归运行效率低，易产生大量变量</li></ul><p>eg. 数列：1，2，3，4…n<br>每一项（除首项）都等于前一项加1，因此有  </p><ul><li>f(n) = f(n-1) + 1 //递归关系</li><li>f(1) = 1 //递归出口<br>所以代码为<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">int function(int n)&#123;    if (n &#x3D;&#x3D; 1)        return 1;    else         return function(n + 1);&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>eg.角谷猜想:n为偶数时，/2，n为奇数时，*3+1，最后总能得到1。<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;int f(int n);static int sum &#x3D; 0;int main()&#123;int a &#x3D; f(5);printf(&quot;%d&quot;, a);return 0;&#125;int f(int n)&#123;if (n &#x3D;&#x3D; 1)return sum;else if (n % 2 &#x3D;&#x3D; 0)&#123;sum++;return f(n &#x2F; 2);&#125;else&#123;sum++;return f(3 * n + 1);&#125;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
